[section#errno
    [:en] Error numbers
]

[para]
[:en]
The header [`<cerrno>] is described in Table [#tab:diagnostics.hdr.cerrno].

[:en]
Its contents are the same as the POSIX header [`<errno.h>], except that [`errno]
shall be defined as a macro.

[enter:note]
[:en]
The intent is to remain in close alignment with the POSIX standard.
[exit:note]

[:en]
A separate [`errno] value shall be provided for each thread.

